				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">i understand the tweaking process, but that doesnt answer my question.
<br />

<br />
and i am not asking be cause i wish to be crowned queen of all pet classes either, yes BL is a pet class.  my question was more along the lines of why would a BL pet have to be par with a mage pet?  we play differently.  i guess i am trying to see how having a bl pet par with a mage pet, and the arsenal of spells you get along with that pet, AND the fact that you can tank with that pet... whereas i need my pet to tank for me so i can even hope to use my spells.
<br />

<br />
in the end result, both classes should be putting out decent dps.  just getting there on different paths.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
